Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:33.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:11.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:13.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,170.389)}Soaring Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(507.167,620.389)}Musasabeedle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosive power\Nis incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosive power of\Nthis brand new liquid fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,will let us power rockets\Nbig enough to reach Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use it as fuel for the\Nrocket test tomorrow in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will a mere 100ccs of this new\Nfuel really power that rocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need it to work,\Nif we ever want rockets to get to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment worked, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Its energy is truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To get that much explosive power\Nfrom just 100ccs of fuel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, Musasabeedle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Capable of 100 meter jumps\Nand 200 meter glides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for you to put those\Nskills of yours to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Musasabeedle,\Nsteal the liquid fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,stored in the warehouse\Nat Osumi Laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may, Great Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with that fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment Osumi\Nconducted this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,proved the incredible\Nexplosive power of that fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The 700ccs still in the\Nwarehouse possess explosive power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,comparable to one\Nkiloton of TNT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We will steal it,\Nand use it to destroy Sapporo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Musasabeedle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that man as a guinea\Npig to test your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A m-monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The slipstream phenomenon:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When Musasabeedle passes\Noverhead at supersonic speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it creates a momentary state\Nof vacuum in the man's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which tears his\Norgans to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone looks mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Yuri and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Off on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who takes a vacation when\Nthere's so much work to be done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Work?\NI don't see any customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He went with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was FBI orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet they've learned something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All matched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, clear the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.73,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Boys be ambitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've come here\Nfirst, huh, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see the whole\Ncity like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki! A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, Yuri.\NHead back to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H1A170A&}Osumi Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker came in here\Nto get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just come\Nbarging in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And what, exactly, is Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have anything that\Nanyone would possibly want here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the liquid fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A m-monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself,\NIchimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you plotting\Nnow, Shocker monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a test, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can experience one\Nkiloton of explosives...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to blow up\Nthe Diet building!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One kiloton?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That little case contains\None kiloton of explosives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have come from\NOsumi Laboratory, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm taking this with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must return with that\Nfuel, no matter what the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We must turn Sapporo\Ninto a wasteland!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we need that liquid fuel to\Nbolster our battle power as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to believe you could blow\Nup the Diet building with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's why\NShocker's after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's crucial\Nfor human advancement,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a dangerous\Nthing you've invented...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A mini-transmitter.\NWe're dealing with Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let our guard\Ndown for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to stop\Nrunning off without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...\NI have my duty to the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you don't need\Nto worry any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If we break it down so it loses its\Nexplosive capability, Shocker can't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you abandoning\Nyour own research?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not abandoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've spent the past three\Nyears on nothing but this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid I\Nneed to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To turn it into plain water...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If a man from the Tokyo Radiation\NCenter arrives, send him to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Radiation Center?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's bringing the special\Nradioactive material, 235,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,which will convert\Nthis fuel into water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to\Nbeat the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\NShocker, in Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how are things\Ngoing on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to recover the new\Nfuel from Shocker, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave now,\NI can make Flight 105 from Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, be there in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Hayato.\NTake it easy until I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry,\Nbut you kids watch the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:41.74,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:52.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3B3CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Chitose Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:56.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H5C6950&}Japan Radiation Center
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the Hokkaido Branch.\NI'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.\NDid someone contact them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this smoke about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought the special radioactive\Nsubstance, 235, that Doctor Osumi asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you're here. Come right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from the Radiation Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recognize you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the phone,\Nthey said they'd be sending one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue Kamen Rider. Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll track that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you lazing around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chairman asked me\Nto watch the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm skipping out,\Nso I needed a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay put for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make the hostages\Nreveal Shocker's base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll really\Nshow up the Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people never learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...\Nthe case is getting further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... Musasabeedle\Nand the combatants split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,45 degrees south, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better take us\Nright to your base!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And no funny business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Showa-Shinzan, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd it get off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not far...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lake Toya, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tobei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to fight back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just finish you\Noff, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...\Nlook there, at Mount Usu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.07,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an7\3c&H525843&}- Shikotsu-Toya National Park\N- Mount Usu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want them dead,\Nhand that case over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Release them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro! All of you, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Rider dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure he's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But with idiots like you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,even the Kamen Rider\Nmight have a rough time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:25.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato, the Kamen\NRider, was able to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:29.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's terrible plan\Nto blow up Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Ichimonji Hayato renewed\Nhis pledge to fight Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,with his wonderful\Nallies by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.63,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,530)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.92,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:46.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the poisonous\Nmonster Kinokomorg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A creature covered in\Npoisonous mushrooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:52.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kinokomorg attacks Kamen Rider\Nwith his terrifying spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:55.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their battle unfolds in a\Nfactory deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:24:00.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "Poisonous\NMonster Kinokomorg Attacks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:00.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}Poisonous Monster\N Kinokomorg Attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:10.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:13.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:15.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:18.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:22.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:25.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:34.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:37.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.62,0:24:41.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:45.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!